Docs.summary: Provides constants and static methods for trigonometric, logarithmic, and other common mathematical functions.

remarks.format: The static fields and methods of the `MathF` class correspond to those of the <xref:System.Math> class, except that their parameters are of type <xref:System.Single> rather than <xref:System.Double>, and they return <xref:System.Single> rather than <xref:System.Double> values.
